{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_001", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "苹果是一种非常常见的水果，口感清脆，味道酸甜，适合直接食用，也可以用于榨汁、烘焙、制作果酱和沙拉。", "citation_locator": "line:5;section:1. 概述;paragraph:1", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_002", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "苹果常被看作日常饮食中最基础的水果之一。", "citation_locator": "line:5;section:1. 概述;paragraph:1", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_003", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "苹果的特点包括：价格相对稳定，购买方便；口感清爽，适合作为加餐水果；含有膳食纤维、维生素和多种植物化合物；既可以生吃，也可以加工成多种食品。", "citation_locator": "line:9;section:1. 概述;paragraph:3", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_004", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "苹果并不是某一种营养素特别突出的水果，但它的优势在于营养比较均衡，适合长期、规律地加入日常饮食。", "citation_locator": "line:16;section:2. 主要营养特点;paragraph:4", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_005", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "苹果中含有一定量的膳食纤维，尤其是果皮部分。", "citation_locator": "line:20;section:2.1 膳食纤维;paragraph:5", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_006", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "膳食纤维有助于增加饱腹感，也有利于维持较好的肠道状态。", "citation_locator": "line:20;section:2.1 膳食纤维;paragraph:5", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_007", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "如果苹果清洗干净，可以连皮一起吃，这样能摄入更多膳食纤维。", "citation_locator": "line:22;section:2.1 膳食纤维;paragraph:6", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_008", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "苹果中含有维生素 C、钾等营养成分。", "citation_locator": "line:26;section:2.2 维生素和矿物质;paragraph:7", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_009", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "苹果的维生素 C 含量通常不如橙子、猕猴桃等水果高。", "citation_locator": "line:26;section:2.2 维生素和矿物质;paragraph:7", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_010", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "苹果中还含有多酚类物质等植物化合物，这类成分通常与水果的颜色、风味和抗氧化特性有关。", "citation_locator": "line:30;section:2.3 植物化合物;paragraph:8", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_011", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "不同品种的苹果在甜度、酸度、硬度和香气上有所区别。", "citation_locator": "line:34;section:3. 常见苹果品种;paragraph:9", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_012", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "红富士甜度较高，口感脆，汁水较多，适合直接食用。", "citation_locator": "line:38;section:3. 常见苹果品种;paragraph:10", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_013", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "嘎啦苹果个头适中，香味明显，口感偏甜，适合直接食用、沙拉。", "citation_locator": "line:39;section:3. 常见苹果品种;paragraph:10", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_014", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "青苹果酸味较明显，口感清爽，适合直接食用、榨汁、烘焙。", "citation_locator": "line:40;section:3. 常见苹果品种;paragraph:10", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_015", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "蛇果外观颜色深红，口感较甜，适合直接食用、摆盘。", "citation_locator": "line:41;section:3. 常见苹果品种;paragraph:10", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_016", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "黄元帅香气明显，口感较软，适合直接食用、制作甜点。", "citation_locator": "line:42;section:3. 常见苹果品种;paragraph:10", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_017", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "苹果适合作为早餐搭配、下午加餐或饭后水果。", "citation_locator": "line:46;section:4. 食用建议;paragraph:11", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_018", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "对于大多数人来说，每天吃一个中等大小的苹果是比较常见的选择。", "citation_locator": "line:46;section:4. 食用建议;paragraph:11", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_019", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "推荐的吃法包括：直接清洗后食用；切块加入酸奶或燕麦中；与胡萝卜、橙子等一起榨汁；切片后用于烘焙；与坚果搭配作为加餐。", "citation_locator": "line:50;section:4. 食用建议;paragraph:13", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_020", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "苹果虽然健康，但也不应该完全替代正餐。合理饮食应该包括主食、蛋白质、蔬菜、水果和适量脂肪。", "citation_locator": "line:56;section:4. 食用建议;paragraph:14", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_021", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "苹果相对耐保存，但不同环境下保存时间差异较大。", "citation_locator": "line:60;section:5. 保存方法;paragraph:15", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_022", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "短时间内食用，可以将苹果放在阴凉、通风处保存，避免阳光直射和高温。", "citation_locator": "line:64;section:5.1 常温保存;paragraph:16", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_023", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "一次购买较多时，可以将苹果放入冰箱冷藏室以延长保存时间并保持口感。", "citation_locator": "line:68;section:5.2 冷藏保存;paragraph:17", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_024", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "苹果会释放乙烯，可能加快一些水果成熟，建议避免与香蕉、猕猴桃等长时间密封放在一起。", "citation_locator": "line:72;section:5.3 避免与部分水果混放;paragraph:18", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_025", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "苹果适合大多数人群食用，包括学生、上班族和老年人，方便携带，适合作为日常健康零食。", "citation_locator": "line:76;section:6. 适合人群与注意事项;paragraph:19", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_026", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "需要注意：胃肠敏感的人空腹吃苹果可能不适；血糖控制要求高的人应注意总水果摄入量；牙齿敏感的人吃偏酸苹果后可漱口；婴幼儿应切小块或做成果泥避免噎食。", "citation_locator": "line:80;section:6. 适合人群与注意事项;paragraph:21", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
{"claim_id": "clm_src_e388858a3d75_llm_027", "source_id": "src_e388858a3d75", "claim_text": "苹果是一种适合长期食用的日常水果，其优势在于购买方便、口感稳定、吃法多样、适合多数人群。", "citation_locator": "line:87;section:7. 简要总结;paragraph:22", "confidence_status": "cited", "created_at": "2026-05-26T10:45:11+00:00"}
